{"word":"G5281 - ὑπομονή - hypomonḗ - hoop-om-on-ay' - Enduring","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπομονή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hypomonḗ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hoop-om-on-ay'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Enduring"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பொறுமை, சகித்தல் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. steadfastness, constancy, endurance"},{"paragraph":"2. a patient, steadfast waiting for"},{"paragraph":"3. a patient enduring, sustaining"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G5278 - ὑπομένω - hypoménō - hoop-om-en'-o/5278\">G5278</a>; cheerful (or hopeful) <i>endurance</i>, <i>constancy:</i> - enduring, patience, patient continuance (waiting)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1696 - ἐμμένω - emménō - em-men'-o/1696\">G1696</a>, <a href=\"#/G3306 - μένω - ménō - men'-o/3306\">G3306</a>, <a href=\"#/G3438 - μονή - monḗ - mon-ay'/3438\">G3438</a>, <a href=\"#/G3887 - παραμένω - paraménō - par-am-en'-o/3887\">G3887</a>, <a href=\"#/G4037 - περιμένω - periménō - per-ee-men'-o/4037\">G4037</a>, <a href=\"#/G5278 - ὑπομένω - hypoménō - hoop-om-en'-o/5278\">G5278</a>, <a href=\"#/G5281 - ὑπομονή - hypomonḗ - hoop-om-on-ay'/5281\">G5281</a>"}]}